Description
	SendMsgQue.c program creates Message queue and asks for input message and sends this message to message queue. ReceiveMsgQue.c program receives the message from message queue and displays the message on terminal.
Note: please run SendMsgQue first and then ReceiveMsgQue in seperate terminals.

Steps to compile
[1] make
	compiles both SendMsgQue.c and ReceiveMsgQue.c 
[2] make clean
	clean up 

Output

Terminal 1

./SendMsgQue 
Please write your message
hi, how are you 
Message Sent!


Terminal 2

./ReceiveMsgQue 
Received Message/s is/are: 
hi, how are you

